The paper discusses security and privacy concerns in IoT data processing and proposes a solution using FIWARE and Intel SGX. This suggests that the paper may belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), information retrieval (cs.IR), or databases (cs.DB). However, since the paper focuses on security and privacy, cs.CR is the most likely category. The other categories are also relevant because they involve aspects of distributed systems, software development, data management, and information retrieval, which are all relevant to the proposed solution.
